President Uhuru Kenyatta has launched the Building Bridges Initiative report at the Bomas of Kenya. He has called on leaders and Kenyans to unite saying "let us now be mature". More than 4,700 delegates from all the 47 counties attended the event. The President asked Kenyans to read and debate the report ahead of a national conference in January. The report ushers a national discussion on the future of Kenya â€” which might shape, too, the Kenyatta succession and the 2022 politics. More follows -Reporting by Hellen Githaiga and Lucas Barasa  